Checkout will be able to do the following:

Read UPC-A barcodes

Store Product Information including location of product, price, distributor, department it belongs to, etc.

Manage Product Inventory

Charge customer for purchases via Cash, Credit Card, and Debit.

View Previous Transactions.


MORE FUNCTIONALITY ON THE WAY

